column1: Thanks everyone for coming out to the first annual Twin Cities Open. Running meets
is always a challenge and is not possible without great help. Thanks to the following
people: (in no particular order) John Bodnar, Joe Cooper, Jim Cahill, Bob Sainati,
Tom Hines, Rich Edinger, Marv Gordon, Dennis Green, Dan Rgnonti, Angela Simons,
Brad Gillingham, Drew Warner, Shawn Cain, Sten Lindquist, Aaron Welborn, Steve Johnson
and the YMCA staff. Thanks to our event sponsors www.safe-usa.com, www.sports-nutrition.com,
Open: Can be any age.               Junior: up to 23 (Dec 31)
